        <h1 class="header">About</h1>
        <p>
          DisrupTutor is a scheduling app to connect students with tutors at the University of West Florida. Our mission
          is to connect students with tutors that match their availability and their needs based on their major, their schedules,
          and their personal preference. This app is a personalized approach to getting one-on-one tutoring for students here at UWF.
        </p>
        <h1>Features</h1>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>Personalized searching and scheduling system to get you a tutor you need, when you need it</li>
            <li>Personalized profile pages for students and tutors to review, rate, and explore tutors</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
